Package civitas.celestis.math.vector

Class Float2

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Number
civitas.celestis.math.vector.Float2
All Implemented Interfaces:
Numeric, FloatVector<Float2>, Vector<Float2>, Packable, Serializable, Comparable<Float2>
public class Float2 extends Number implements FloatVector<Float2>, Packable
An immutable two-dimensional vector which uses floats to represent its components.

2D float vectors can be packed into a single long for easier storage. No precision is lost in the process.
